# App Store Pre-Check Plugin

A Claude plugin that validates Flutter/mobile apps against Apple App Store and Google Play Store requirements before submission.

## Features

- **Automated scanning** of `Info.plist`, `build.gradle`, and source code
- **Catches common rejection reasons** from real-world experience
- **Generates manual checklist** for items requiring human verification
- **Supports Flutter** (with extensibility for React Native/Expo)

## Checks Performed

### iOS (Info.plist)
| Check | Guideline |
|-------|-----------|
| UIBackgroundModes audit | 2.5.4 |
| Privacy purpose strings validation | 5.1.1 |
| App Transport Security | - |
| Required permission keys | 5.1.1 |

### iOS (App Features)
| Check | Guideline |
|-------|-----------|
| Account deletion requirement | 5.1.1(v) |
| Restore Purchases for IAP | 3.1.1 |
| Privacy Policy accessibility | 5.1.1 |

### Android
| Check | Requirement |
|-------|-------------|
| Target SDK level | API 35 (new apps) |
| Signing configuration | Play App Signing |
| Build format | AAB required |

### Code Analysis
- Login/account creation detection
- Account deletion implementation
- In-app purchase packages
- Restore purchases functionality

## Installation

Add to your Claude plugin marketplace or use standalone:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/frpaf/app-store-precheck.git
```

## Usage

### Via Claude

Ask Claude to:
- "Pre-check my app before submission"
- "Validate my Flutter app for App Store"
- "Check for Play Store compliance issues"

### Standalone Script

```bash
cd /path/to/your/flutter/project
bash skills/precheck/scripts/precheck.sh
```

## Output

The plugin generates a report with:
- ❌ **Blockers**: Issues that will definitely cause rejection
- ⚠️ **Warnings**: Issues that may cause rejection
- ✅ **Passed**: Checks that passed validation
- 📋 **Manual Checklist**: Items requiring human verification

## Based On

This plugin was created from lessons learned during real App Store reviews, including issues like:

1. UIBackgroundModes "audio" rejection (not valid for notification sounds)
2. Generic camera purpose string rejection
3. Backend API downtime during review
4. Android signing configuration issues
5. Missing account deletion with login present
6. Missing Restore Purchases with IAP present

## Structure

```
app-store-precheck/
├── .claude-plugin/
│   └── plugin.json           # Plugin metadata
├── skills/
│   └── precheck/
│       ├── SKILL.md          # Main skill documentation
│       ├── scripts/
│       │   └── precheck.sh   # Automated scanner
│       └── evals/
│           └── evals.json    # Test cases
└── README.md
```

